				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">SOE isn't going to make pets much stronger than they already are. They're just afraid to say so because too many people will quit, so they are content to keep stringing us along, pretending to discuss the issue for several months.
<br />

<br />
Pet foci could definitely scale a little better, but in terms of balance, a high end raiding mage already has at least twice the hp, mana, mana regen, better focus effects for spells, etc when compared to the non-raiding mage. The high end pet doesn't <span style="font-style: italic">need</span> to be twice as good as the unfocused/dpoc pets, though it does need to scale.<br />_________________<br />Naladini
